Text: Label Your Way Out of Chaos Palm Solutions brought to you by InSync Online Label Your Way Out of Chaos Dear Jess A mailing to get out the door corporate videos to label and deliver file drawers jammed so full you couldnt pry them open with a crowbar Can you say chaos Better to say DYMO LabelWriter EL the easy way to organize your office and your life This powerful versatile PC printer is compatible with Palmtm Desktop Its also a snap to use Simply access the LabelWriter software through your Palmtm Desktop to choose from more than different labels for printing addresses media name tags and file folders No more trips to the post officethe EL even prints Internet postage You can also print addresses and contacts stored in Microsoft Word Outlook Goldmine ACT and CardScan And you wont spend a cent on toner or ink cartridges because The EL uses thermal print technology Find out more udvkeSQOecZxb The InSync Online Team The content of this message is based on your personal InSync Online profile To modify your profile or unsubscribe from InSync Online return to your InSync Online profile by clicking on the link below Or unsubscribe by replying to this message with unsubscribe as the subject line of the message C Palm Inc All rights reserved udkeSQOecZxQ Palmcom udvEeSQOecZxV Palm Store udvEeSQOecZxK InSync Online insyncdynisZVae MyPalm udyEeSQOecZxE
